{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775893829937,"sessionID":"ses_2847add1cffeuUuNzOXxl3iH5B","part":{"id":"prt_d7b8558fd001ORE0NK0Hi0Bvkr","messageID":"msg_d7b854cfd001xrMxVN3M0EM3QT","sessionID":"ses_2847add1cffeuUuNzOXxl3iH5B","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-a6301ee142f843019bfc3dca71243a5c","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/tasks.md","limit":100},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-038 Implementation Plan\n2: \n3: **Feature:** AR-038 — Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager)\n4: **Goal:** 为 pkg/workloadmanager 模块编写全面的单元测试，确保所有核心组件、控制器、处理器和工具函数都有充分的测试覆盖。\n5: **Acceptance Criteria:**\n6: - 所有核心组件（controller、handler、client、gc、auth、middleware、config、api）都有对应的 *_test.go 文件\n7: - 测试覆盖率 >80%\n8: - 所有测试可通过 `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` 运行\n9: - 测试遵循 testify/assert 和 mock 的使用模式\n10: - 测试用例覆盖正常流程、边界条件和错误场景\n11: - 遵循 test_spec.md 中定义的测试用例（TestCase-WM-001, TestCase-WM-002, TestCase-WM-003）\n12: **Architecture:** Go 单元测试，使用 testify 框架，fake k8s client\n13: **Tech Stack:** Go 1.21+, testify, k8s.io/client-go/testing\n14: **Frontend validation:** No\n15: \n16: ---\n17: \n18: ### Task 1: 验证现有测试并更新 gc/collector_test.go\n19: \n20: **Files:**\n21: - Verify: `pkg/workloadmanager/gc/collector_test.go`\n22: - Verify: `pkg/workloadmanager/gc/collector.go`\n23: \n24: **Step 1: Review existing tests**\n25: \n26: 确认现有测试用例的正确性和完整性。\n27: \n28: **Step 2: Add missing test cases**\n29: \n30: ```go\n31: // pkg/workloadmanager/gc/collector_test.go\n32: \n33: func TestGCCollector_Collect_StoreError(t *testing.T) {\n34:     mockStore := &mockStore{}\n35:     scheme := runtime.NewScheme()\n36:     scheme.AddKnownTypes(schema.GroupVersion{Group: \"agents.x-k8s.io\", Version: \"v1alpha1\"}, \n37:         &unstructured.Unstructured{},\n38:         &unstructured.UnstructuredList{},\n39:     )\n40:     \n41:     fakeClient := fake.NewSimpleDynamicClientWithCustomListKinds(scheme, map[schema.GroupVersionResource]string{\n42:         SandboxGVR: \"SandboxList\",\n43:         SandboxClaimGVR: \"SandboxClaimList\",\n44:     })\n45: \n46:     sessionID := \"test-session\"\n47:     \n48:     mockStore.On(\"GetSandbox\", mock.Anything, sessionID).Return(nil, fmt.Errorf(\"store error\"))\n49: \n50:     sandbox := buildTestSandbox(\"test-sandbox\", \"default\", sessionID, 24*time.Hour)\n51:     fakeClient.Resource(SandboxGVR).Namespace(\"default\").Create(context.Background(), sandbox, metav1.CreateOptions{})\n52: \n53:     config := DefaultGCConfig()\n54:     policy, _ := NewGCPolicy(config)\n55:     metrics := NewGCMetrics()\n56: \n57:     collector := NewGCCollector(fakeClient, mockStore, config, policy, metrics)\n58: \n59:     ctx := context.Background()\n60:     result, err := collector.Collect(ctx)\n61: \n62:     assert.NoError(t, err)\n63:     assert.NotNil(t, result)\n64:     assert.Equal(t, 1, result.Scanned)\n65:     assert.Equal(t, 0, result.Candidates)\n66:     assert.Equal(t, 0, result.Deleted)\n67:     assert.Equal(t, 1, result.Errors)\n68: }\n69: \n70: func TestGCCollector_Delete_StoreError(t *testing.T) {\n71:     mockStore := &mockStore{}\n72:     scheme := runtime.NewScheme()\n73:     scheme.AddKnownTypes(schema.GroupVersion{Group: \"agents.x-k8s.io\", Version: \"v1alpha1\"}, \n74:         &unstructured.Unstructured{},\n75:         &unstructured.UnstructuredList{},\n76:     )\n77:     \n78:     fakeClient := fake.NewSimpleDynamicClientWithCustomListKinds(scheme, map[schema.GroupVersionResource]string{\n79:         SandboxGVR: \"SandboxList\",\n80:     })\n81: \n82:     sessionID := \"test-session\"\n83:     \n84:     mockStore.On(\"DeleteSandboxBySessionID\", mock.Anything, sessionID).Return(fmt.Errorf(\"store delete error\"))\n85: \n86:     sandbox := buildTestSandbox(\"test-sandbox\", \"default\", sessionID, 10*time.Minute)\n87:     fakeClient.Resource(SandboxGVR).Namespace(\"default\").Create(context.Background(), sandbox, metav1.CreateOptions{})\n88: \n89:     config := DefaultGCConfig()\n90:     policy, _ := NewGCPolicy(config)\n91:     metrics := NewGCMetrics()\n92: \n93:     collector := NewGCCollector(fakeClient, mockStore, config, policy, metrics)\n94: \n95:     ctx := context.Background()\n96:     err := collector.Delete(ctx, sandbox, wmTypes.CleanupReasonExpired)\n97: \n98:     assert.NoError(t, err)\n99:     mockStore.AssertExpectations(t)\n100: }\n\n(Showing lines 1-100 of 2480. Use offset=101 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-038 Implementation Plan\n\n**Feature:** AR-038 — Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager)\n**Goal:** 为 pkg/workloadmanager 模块编写全面的单元测试，确保所有核心组件、控制器、处理器和工具函数都有充分的测试覆盖。\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- 所有核心组件（controller、handler、client、gc、auth、middleware、config、api）都有对应的 *_test.go 文件\n- 测试覆盖率 >80%\n- 所有测试可通过 `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` 运行\n- 测试遵循 testify/assert 和 mock 的使用模式\n- 测试用例覆盖正常流程、边界条件和错误场景\n- 遵循 test_spec.md 中定义的测试用例（TestCase-WM-001, TestCase-WM-002, TestCase-WM-003）\n**Architecture:** Go 单元测试，使用 testify 框架，fake k8s client\n**Tech Stack:** Go 1.21+, testify, k8s.io/client-go/testing\n**Frontend validation:** No\n\n---\n\n### Task 1: 验证现有测试并更新 gc/collector_test.go\n\n**Files:**","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775893829911,"end":1775893829935}}}}
